Showcasing colourblock pattern and a retro-inspired tiered design, this purple dress from Sangria is all about style and elegance. Made from cotton, this dress has a round neck, short sleeves and a front button placket that make it visually appealing, while the flared cut lends a flattering silhouette. This dress can be styled with a pair of white sneakers to look your best.&nbsp;Colourblock pattern&nbsp;Tiered design&nbsp;Front button placket&nbsp;
